page.title: 06The Ponds in Henham
page.content: There are four main ponds in Henham Three ponds are murky and one pond is clear. In the clear pond there are froglets and tadpoles and fish.By the ponds there are trees and flowers.We found Mothers die,Buttercup,Thistle, Daffodil,Cowparsley, Sweetcicely,Willowleavedpeartree,Pubwo rt,Milroil,White willow,Gipsywort,. There was lots of pond weed in the three murky ponds.There were 17 ducks and two ducklings on the ponds in June 1985.There was litter in the clear pond mainly sweet wrappers.The clear pond was 10mx42m.The other ponds were 15mx48m , 11mx10m and 10mx10m.Many families feed the ducks on the ponds but same ducks are run over each year .By the ponds is a sign saying "Drive carefully-Beware of the ducks".
